{"tid":1039666,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你地相信the best is yet to come定柏拉圖麥穗愛情論?","createTime":"2019-02-27T14:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T13:08:33.000Z","uid":76310,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dc8d37f7c6ede6bec9a437bd0ed0c3b6e463b30c","tid":1039666,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T14:29:59.000Z","msg":"the best is yet to come:<br />\n最好的尚末來臨, 相信會明天更好<br />\n<br />\n柏拉圖麥穗愛情論:<br />\n有一天, 柏拉圖問蘇格拉底甚麼是愛情, 蘇格拉底便叫柏拉圖在麥田走一回, 不許回頭, 只能摘一回, 去挑出一棵最大的麥穗. 結果柏拉圖卻空手而回. 柏拉圖說：<br />\n看到不錯時, 不知是不是最好, 所以沒有摘; 但當繼續走下去時, 卻發現總是不及之前的好. 原來最好的麥穗已經錯過.<br />\n愛情是一種理想的追求. 可惜時間卻是流動不等人的, 誰也不能「將光陰倒轉, 再讓往日復現眼前」. 你不會在同一時間遇上所有人, 也不一定在「對的時間」遇上「對的人」, 一錯過便沒有. <br />\n<br />\n你相信那一個?"},{"pid":"d8c2a12fe8195a3ec1de853408cdaeac78b6109e","tid":1039666,"uid":43575,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T14:35:43.000Z","msg":"好似我咁多人追既人，一定揀 the best is yet to cume"},{"pid":"9de1d525d9cd1ad7ffc3bc404b1c78ec94e9a03d","tid":1039666,"uid":7343,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"相信nothing is coming"},{"pid":"2205f13ac929ccd887dd5be9f6c56ff6fa9cf9be","tid":1039666,"uid":218405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9de1d525d9cd1ad7ffc3bc404b1c78ec94e9a03d","tid":1039666,"uid":7343,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"相信nothing is coming"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T15:15:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f64d462b217c9ba6693778720047cbf48c6581b","tid":1039666,"uid":24660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T15:28:06.000Z","msg":"樂觀SIR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301355b3385cdcb6966ccbc232d85b5267908594","tid":1039666,"uid":218575